V:= \{ f: \mathbb{R} \mapsto \mathbb{R}\ |\ \exists\ {a_0},...{a_4} \in \mathbb{R}\ : f(x)=\sum_{i=0}^{4}{a_ix^i} \ \forall \ x \in \mathbb{R}\}
\phi(f)(x)=f''(x)+x \cdot f'(x) - f(x+1)
